    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wood of several trees belonging to the genus Juglans, ranging in color from grey-brown to purple brown, used in making cabinetwork, veneer, butts and rifle stocks. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
